item.title: Tony Williams Drum Clinic
item.description:
Tony Williams Drum Clinic

This is a very rare Tony Williams Clinic at the Zildjian drummer festival. This used to be up on Google video but i could not find it anymore so I decided to upload it on here for everyone to enjoy. I go back to watch this whenever i feel uninspired.

item.title: Quantum Mechanics Explained
item.description:
Quantum Mechanics Explained

Want to know everything to know about quantum mechanics? Well check out this excellent video by Eugene Khutoryansky if you do. Eugene covers things like EPR / Bell inequality, the relationship between measurement and entanglement and wave particle duality for some but there's much more here too. Love the cat btw.
